{"title":"红灯颂","authors":["牛小白"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红灯颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛小白"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金线缠，银线扎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大红的灯罩贴金花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红灯糊好为什嘛？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门上高高挂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红灯高、红满天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四面八方齐来看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又照近、又照远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照耀人民四万万。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红灯红、放光明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好比天上的北斗星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕雨、不怕风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新中国挂上了翻身灯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红灯最属那个亮？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一盏红灯挂中央，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照见了咱们的领袖像。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席—你比红灯红！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席—你比红灯亮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四九、十、三"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}